  "desc": {
    "en": "Three warm spot lights fire into thin fog. Once the light scatters through it, the beams themselves become visible.",
    "zh": "三盞暖色聚光燈打進一團薄霧，光線經過霧氣散射之後，光束本身就變得可見。"
  },
  "tip": {
    "en": "Denser fog makes the beams more visible but lengthens render times. Density is a trade-off between mood and speed.",
    "zh": "霧的濃度越高，光束越明顯，但算圖時間也會拉長，濃度是氛圍與效率之間的取捨。"
  },
